<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Reset Password Dashboard IKU</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f2f7f3;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#1c2b23;">
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background:#f2f7f3;padding:24px 12px;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="max-width:680px;background:#ffffff;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #dbe8de;">
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#17624a,#1f7d5f);">
                <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding:28px 28px 18px 28px;color:#ffffff;">
                      <p style="margin:0;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:1.4px;text-transform:uppercase;opacity:.88;">Dashboard IKU Fasilkom</p>
                      <h1 style="margin:10px 0 0 0;font-size:28px;line-height:1.25;">Permintaan Reset Password</h1>
                      <p style="margin:10px 0 0 0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;opacity:.95;">Hai {{name}}, kami menerima permintaan untuk mengatur ulang password akun Anda.</p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td style="padding:24px 28px;">
                <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:#375044;">
                  Demi keamanan akun, silakan gunakan tombol di bawah ini. Tautan reset hanya berlaku sampai:
                </p>
                <p style="margin:0 0 18px 0;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#17624a;">{{expiredAt}}</p>

                <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="margin:0 0 20px 0;">
                  <tr>
                    <td align="center" style="border-radius:10px;background:#17624a;">
                      <a href="{{resetUrl}}" style="display:inline-block;padding:12px 22px;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.2px;">Atur Ulang Password Sekarang</a>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>

                <div style="background:#f7fbf9;border:1px dashed #b8d7c9;border-radius:10px;padding:14px;">
                  <p style="margin:0;font-size:12px;line-height:1.8;color:#4a6357;">
                    Jika tombol tidak bisa diklik, salin tautan berikut ke browser:<br />
                    <a href="{{resetUrl}}" style="color:#17624a;word-break:break-word;">{{resetUrl}}</a>
                  </p>
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td style="padding:0 28px 20px 28px;">
                <h2 style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:15px;color:#17624a;">Panduan Keamanan</h2>
                <ul style="margin:0;padding-left:18px;color:#536b5f;font-size:13px;line-height:1.8;">
                  <li>Jangan bagikan tautan reset ke siapa pun.</li>
                  <li>Gunakan password unik minimal 8 karakter.</li>
                  <li>Jika Anda tidak meminta reset, abaikan email ini.</li>
                </ul>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td style="background:#f8fbff;padding:16px 28px;border-top:1px solid #e4efe7;">
                <p style="margin:0;font-size:12px;line-height:1.7;color:#607a6d;">
                  Email ini dikirim otomatis oleh sistem {{appName}}.<br />
                  Butuh bantuan? Hubungi administrator sistem.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
